---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About BenefitsCheck UK"
  description="BenefitsCheck UK is a free, independent resource that helps people across the UK find out which benefits they may be entitled to. Updated for 2026/27 rates."
>
  <div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 2rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;">
    <a href="/" style="font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1f;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">← Back to home</a>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;color:#1a1a1a;margin:1.5rem 0 1rem;line-height:1.2;">About BenefitsCheck UK</h1>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">BenefitsCheck UK is a free, independent resource that helps people across the UK find out which benefits they may be entitled to. Our free checkers cover 8 key benefit areas: Universal Credit, PIP, Carer's Allowance, Council Tax Reduction, Housing Benefit, Child Benefit, Pension Credit, and benefits for people who are sick or disabled.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">We also publish plain-English guides to help you understand how the UK benefits system works — who qualifies, how to claim, and what to watch out for.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">All calculations use 2026/27 DWP and HMRC rates. Results are estimates only — your actual entitlement is determined by DWP and HMRC based on a full assessment.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">Nothing you enter is stored, tracked, or shared. All calculations happen entirely in your browser.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Disclaimer</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">This tool provides estimates only and is not financial advice. Always verify your entitlement on GOV.UK or with Citizens Advice before making any claim decisions.</p>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#888;margin-top:2rem;">Rates last verified: July 2026</p>
  </div>
</Base>
